text:
Order the Penang fried Kway teow to try.
They used the thin kway teow, ingredients includes fish cake and 2 prawns. Find not sufficient oil and drak sauce seem too little. Woh Hei not there and could tasted some over burn over the food.
The carrot cake is crispy and flavourful hard to find such a nice white cake in Singapore , recommended to eat with chilli
It’s always filled with egg shell. That’s why the businesss getting lesser and lesser
